				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-minh-tinh-h%E1%BA%ADu-di%E1%BB%87n-nh%E1%BA%A5t-tuy%E1%BB%87t/poem-bgF0qd2C7NS8mU2S2QfqNw">Đề minh tinh hậu diện nhất tuyệt - 題銘旌後面一絕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Thi%C3%AAn-Hu%C3%A2n/Lan-k%E1%BB%B3-06/poem-3QHzu55u69aE_C3PcNEpWg">Lan kỳ 06 - 蘭其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Thi%C3%AAn-Hu%C3%A2n/author-dgO_tJsVrUseJlMi0oK--w">Tạ Thiên Huân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Long-M%C3%B4n-tr%E1%BA%A5n/poem-Ecjy8fs4G7pDuf9-E3x_-Q">Long Môn trấn - 龍門鎮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-xu%C3%A2n-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-t%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ABm-th%E1%BA%A3o-%E1%BB%91c-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-yFnvaZPTU72YXot7sCjUtw">Mộ xuân đề Nhương Tây tân nhẫm thảo ốc kỳ 1 - 暮春題瀼西新賃草屋其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Ph%C3%B9-Phong-h%C3%A0o-s%C4%A9-ca/poem-3VA4D7IRvvruv2gGIxG8GA">Phù Phong hào sĩ ca - 扶風豪士歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%E1%BB%91ng-b%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh/poem-Wg0ot4FW2PMgi-jPSv_v0g">Tống bắc sứ Sài Trang Khanh - 送北使柴莊卿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-X3Oume1_mYQvTGcgMAhydQ">Trần Quang Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tr%E1%BA%AFc-h%E1%BB%99-1/poem-6cJ8Xb0efN7tN3QFhHRGcQ">Trắc hộ 1 - 陟岵 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/Tr%C3%BA-Ho%C3%A0i-An-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Ho%C3%A0i-%C3%82m-h%E1%BA%A7u-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-3jDauQx9ioP4SofHoXoMnw">Trú Hoài An phỏng Hoài Âm hầu điếu đài - 駐淮安訪淮陰侯釣臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/author-YDc3orDW4enWycHMfed3Ww">Lê Quý Đôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ZDB2Tl5514uy8PI478SU_g">Vương Chiêu Quân kỳ 1 - 王昭君其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
